<h2 id="head-f90ce69a26d1e769c731c46fb26374a893645a92">The Primary Schools</h2>
<p>
There are 11 primary schools of magic. These each use their own spell books to cast a spell, and each has its own spells, of varying kind. These spells and their effects are described in each page.  The 11 schools are: 
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 <a href="./Documentation_2fMagic_2fSchools_2fAir">/Air</a> 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
