    </ul>


<p>
<a id="Secondary"/> <h2 id="head-78e19681fde069a47e7354ce98d4d94b8885a9b7">The Secondary 'M'agic schools</h2>

</p>
<p>
Other magical skills, primarily used by characters of a specific class are. The details and special characteristics of each are outlined in these pages:  
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
